{"tid":132500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"朝鮮不點名批中國貿易制裁：常自稱友好鄰國隨美國音樂起舞","createTime":"2017-02-24T01:08:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-25T18:13:06.000Z","uid":20933,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"47efd01b666f855e760fcea4ae45f3753d2827e2","tid":132500,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T01:08:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170224/s00004/1487897324027SL4_BECEDB92DCF80C1008E1AB9AB1B1C874.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170224%2Fs00004%2F1487897324027SL4_BECEDB92DCF80C1008E1AB9AB1B1C874.jpg&h=8942dd4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國上周宣布禁止朝鮮的煤炭進口，以制裁朝鮮持續進行彈道導彈測試。朝鮮官方媒體朝中社發表評論，指摘中國對美國的要求讓步。 <br />\n<br />\n文章沒有點名中國，但提到「一個經常說自己是朝鮮友好的鄰國」，又稱「這國國家，自以為是個大國，卻隨美國音樂起舞」。<br />\n<br />\n文章批評中國「採取非人道步驟，如阻止全部的外貿」，這有助於朝鮮敵人拖垮其社會制度，又指認為切斷資金，朝鮮就不會製造核武器和洲際彈道導彈的想法很幼稚。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普接受路透社訪問則指，如果中國有心解決北韓問題，事件將會變得非常簡單。<br />\n<br />\n（英國廣播公司/路透社）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170224/s00004/1487897474692\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170224%2Fs00004%2F1487897474692&d=Xx1rX%2BBWBBKZa4OSQyufSUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=785d02e9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170224%2Fs00004%2F1487897474692&h=df927baa\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170224/s00004/1487897474692</a>"},{"pid":"b76c224c53b0acee52e13bb1c24c07ec7aaec05b","tid":132500,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T01:09:01.000Z","msg":"個tone同支那一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1753e50c694b71612bbf81b3017931ccb9f14a4c","tid":132500,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T01:15:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16f34c0b3c04afe2a7e34eeec5f6a8c4857cf6a0","tid":132500,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T01:16:44.000Z","msg":"金仔同美帝fd 好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adbd33ab38c07c8e8b6470abf00fac6a0acc06c8","tid":132500,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T01:16:45.000Z","msg":"支持金仔射粒導彈過去俾佢地試下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"534aa050636ec849236e1b56078167c597c6cc98","tid":132500,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T01:17:37.000Z","msg":"中國商務部上星期六宣布，全面禁止從北韓進口煤礦。北韓官方朝中社不點名批評中國實施的制裁。朝中社在評論表示，有口口聲聲標榜「友好鄰邦」的周邊國家，說北韓的核技術只是初級階段，刻意貶低北韓在今個月12日成功發射的北極星2型彈道導彈的意義。<br />\n<br />\n文章又批評對方，以毫無法律依據的聯合國「制裁決議」為由，肆無忌憚地採取非人道措施，全面斷絕涉及改善民生的對外貿易，實際上同敵對勢力要搞垮北韓制度的陰謀大同小異。文章表示，一個以大國自居的國家，沒有政治主見，對美國隨波逐流，卻辯稱要制止核計劃，以為只要切斷小小的資金，就會令北韓無法製作核武和洲際彈道導彈，這個想法是幼稚可笑。"},{"pid":"f71962dd4ad01d25d6e0458f3a9468f8371f41e0","tid":132500,"uid":2521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T01:20:38.000Z","msg":"金仔依翻說話好正<br />\n唔知愛面子ge中國人會點諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b429d5c3c175295a491790f64f38d86e80e74c04","tid":132500,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T01:25:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"5437e6b8a579ecb57a1fdeca371cd628525e5c09","tid":132500,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T01:25:31.000Z","msg":"點知北韓原來暗交美國"},{"pid":"1f432b55fd742db2f6d9cae0eb7bb8f6769a787c","tid":132500,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T01:27:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>金仔依翻說話好正<br />\n唔知愛面子ge中國人會點諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n「我哋唔俾錢佢 佢等執粒啦，到時睇下邊個求邊個先」"},{"pid":"34a550141029dfd0408f55c5b57ab3fd0b214a9e","tid":132500,"uid":24345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T02:07:47.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗共產黨不嬲都係咁柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b6fbaf70b2207c3a79a8547c16dc60257cce16e","tid":132500,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T03:06:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2184e7b8a47248ffecc877738f3a4574b04235c0","tid":132500,"uid":31098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T03:54:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n文章沒有點名中國，但提到「<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一個經常說自己是朝鮮友好的鄰國</span></strong>」，又稱「這國國家，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">自以為是個大國</span></strong>，卻隨美國音樂起舞」。<br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一語中的，好波 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7c7650bbe9518936207052a7e66ab854c82f75b","tid":132500,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T11:37:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>金仔同美帝fd 好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實北韓早幾年真係想投靠美國<br />\n<br />\n但唔知點解無成事<br />\n<br />\n個人估計係因為北韓太廢太柒, 連美國都唔想收留佢"},{"pid":"f88018359b708a1f0e1f3aa988f4af09920238b8","tid":132500,"uid":27605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T17:34:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支持金仔射粒導彈過去俾佢地試下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nOn9先講得出ed野 你想死炸仆街 我未架"},{"pid":"7b4